#: ../../architecture.rst:2 0ae637f1477f4d00a635434f66ca27e1
msgid "Architecture"
msgstr "Architecture"

#: ../../architecture.rst:4 d2722d52fe7943d78f3113833ec69db8
msgid "This page describes RansomLook from three complementary angles:"
msgstr "Cette page décrit RansomLook sous trois angles complémentaires :"

#: ../../architecture.rst:6 b8c8563f19f24056b5efbff368c20416
msgid ""
"a **functional view** — what the project does, independent of any "
"technology;"
msgstr ""
"une **vue fonctionnelle** — ce que fait le projet, indépendamment de la "
"technologie ;"

#: ../../architecture.rst:7 6dc0a295f157421da2fdc3bb08a2b9f0
msgid ""
"an **architectural view** — the technical components, available at two "
"zoom levels (high-level and ultra-detailed);"
msgstr ""
"une **vue architecturale** — les composants techniques, à deux niveaux de"
" zoom (haut niveau et ultra détaillée) ;"

#: ../../architecture.rst:9 70abb163eb924217ac3d5be9d451f955
msgid ""
"a **user view** — five typical journeys from the perspective of the main "
"personas."
msgstr ""
"une **vue utilisateur** — cinq parcours typiques du point de vue des "
"principaux personas."

#: ../../architecture.rst:16 39709f2d26c84732aa7ec09f0c90df9b
msgid "Functional view"
msgstr "Vue fonctionnelle"

#: ../../architecture.rst:18 02a9d2e5f8a94afa9d92ce28c55293be
msgid ""
"From upstream sources (leak sites, public leak databases, ransom-notes "
"corpora, crypto trackers) through the processing pipeline, to the "
"deliverables exposed to operators."
msgstr ""
"Des sources en amont (leak sites, bases de leaks publiques, corpus de "
"notes de rançon, trackers crypto) jusqu'aux livrables exposés aux "
"opérateurs, en passant par le pipeline de traitement."

#: ../../architecture.rst:63 49d403b4af63446aa5633fafa8b6d87f
msgid "Key points:"
msgstr "Points clés :"

#: ../../architecture.rst:65 ce389712f822474d9ae3ac8f43a3363b
msgid ""
"Every source is pulled (not pushed) — RansomLook is a read-only "
"aggregator."
msgstr ""
"Chaque source est tirée (pas poussée) — RansomLook est un agrégateur en "
"lecture seule."

#: ../../architecture.rst:66 cc134b08d6f04898aa198a80435ab911
msgid ""
"The pipeline is **idempotent**: re-running scrape/parse on the same input"
" converges to the same state."
msgstr ""
"Le pipeline est **idempotent** : relancer scrape/parse sur les mêmes "
"entrées converge vers le même état."

#: ../../architecture.rst:68 59a3c46a7ce1459a8a52a5719e7fcfd0
msgid ""
"The four deliverables share a single data store — the web UI and the API "
"expose identical facts."
msgstr ""
"Les quatre livrables partagent un seul data store — l'UI web et l'API "
"exposent les mêmes faits."

#: ../../architecture.rst:72 ffc6d62f5b6d4f5bb2671ff61fafd15e
msgid "Architectural view — high-level"
msgstr "Vue architecturale — haut niveau"

#: ../../architecture.rst:74 e6b2b349c8c34deda4fdd322e491f16e
msgid "The technical boundaries at a glance."
msgstr "Les limites techniques en un coup d'œil."

#: ../../architecture.rst:105 cd2492d3d1f04714983c9df370d38e4c
msgid "Architectural view — ultra-detailed"
msgstr "Vue architecturale — ultra détaillée"

#: ../../architecture.rst:107 9df8154d1bf9403f956cd5c98078b006
msgid ""
"Every process, data store and external dependency actually present in a "
"running RansomLook instance."
msgstr ""
"Chaque processus, data store et dépendance externe effectivement présents"
" dans une instance en marche."

#: ../../architecture.rst:215 28d05447f1154b2c9413b0bdb2871cf0
msgid ""
"Workers run as cron-driven or systemd-timed jobs. They share the Valkey "
"instance and filesystem but never talk to each other directly — "
"coordination is implicit through data in Valkey."
msgstr ""
"Les workers tournent en cron ou timers systemd. Ils partagent l'instance "
"Valkey et le système de fichiers mais ne se parlent jamais directement — "
"la coordination est implicite via les données dans Valkey."

#: ../../architecture.rst:220 3020aee519af4421a3e326796bcbb86f
msgid "User view — five journeys"
msgstr "Vue utilisateur — cinq parcours"

#: ../../architecture.rst:222 54a376980d5d45a68785c011c169ab15
msgid "Typical flows for the five personas documented on :doc:`about <features>`."
msgstr ""
"Parcours typiques pour les cinq personas documentés sur :doc:`about "
"<features>`."

#: ../../architecture.rst:225 6a89b1da282c43418d9a05a92f87aed7
msgid "SOC / IR — match an observed URL"
msgstr "SOC / IR — identifier une URL observée"

#: ../../architecture.rst:227 92926d60dc5b4a1cb9adc1924c420cff
msgid ""
"Starting from a suspicious URL spotted on an endpoint, confirm whether it"
" is a known ransomware mirror and take blocking action."
msgstr ""
"À partir d'une URL suspecte repérée sur un endpoint, confirmer s'il "
"s'agit d'un miroir ransomware connu et prendre des mesures de blocage."

#: ../../architecture.rst:241 c2ea47fed2d64e0aa1757eaa633e2bcd
msgid "CTI analyst — weekly trend report"
msgstr "Analyste CTI — rapport de tendance hebdomadaire"

#: ../../architecture.rst:243 e0f64db0d6254cdeab9bb4cdd0741daf
msgid "Build a weekly \"state of ransomware\" briefing."
msgstr "Construire un briefing hebdomadaire « état du ransomware »."

#: ../../architecture.rst:256 7a188c5199ec4e29a103857bdb1abf8a
msgid "CSIRT / national CERT — constituency triage"
msgstr "CSIRT / CERT national — triage de la constituence"

#: ../../architecture.rst:258 f80ab75310784e8e95d12841006cd94e
msgid "Morning scan for new victims inside the constituency."
msgstr ""
"Balayage matinal à la recherche de nouvelles victimes dans la "
"constituence."

#: ../../architecture.rst:271 a32d97e1531145c78ea20f78ba4da0ca
msgid "Security researcher — actor investigation"
msgstr "Chercheur en sécurité — investigation sur un acteur"

#: ../../architecture.rst:273 adb7479e84fc44b9b4463236cc5efa86
msgid "Investigate a named actor, trace their relations."
msgstr "Enquêter sur un acteur nommé, tracer ses relations."

#: ../../architecture.rst:286 df389bd44d1e458eb4f0127c337708a8
msgid "Integrator — automation & dashboards"
msgstr "Intégrateur — automatisation et dashboards"

#: ../../architecture.rst:288 c71841224089424ab0c3ab7448653e26
msgid "Build a live dashboard or feed data into a SIEM."
msgstr "Construire un dashboard en direct ou alimenter un SIEM."

#: ../../architecture.rst:301 0e6ce57eeeaa4e97ac90f44eaf5ab087
msgid "Editing the diagrams"
msgstr "Éditer les diagrammes"

